node.text:
In the centenary year of the House, Gucci celebrated its Aria collection through a special fashion show held at the Shanghai Exhibition Centre in China, recreating the set and atmosphere of the #GucciAria film, co-directed by @floriasigismondi and @alessandro_michele, which debuted earlier this year in April. 
#AlessandroMichele
Music:
The soundtrack, by Alessandro Michele and mixed by Lawrence Rothman, comprises a selection of songs 
featuring the word Gucci, speaking to the staying power of the Maison and how profusely it contributed to 
the vocabulary of pop culture.
Lil Pump "Gucci Gang”
(B. Murray / G. Garcia / G. G. Nealy)
Rick Ross feat. Future “Green Gucci Suit”
(R. Ross / A. Stewart / N. Wilburn / D. Hayes)

Bhad Bhabie “Gucci Flip Flops (feat. Lil Yachty)”
(M. McCollum / L. Jae / I. Whitlow / J. Muhammad / L. Porter / D. McCorkell / D. Bregoli / S. Gloade / J. 
Lowe)
Mier “Gucci On My Bag”
Die Antwoord, Dita Von Teese “Gucci Coochie”
(A. Du Toit / W. Jones / J. Nobrega / L. Muggard / Dita Von Teese)
Vitalic, feat. David Shaw “Waiting For The Stars”
(P. Arbez / D. Shaw/ J. Garraud)

node.title: Gucci Aria Fashion Show in Shanghai

node.text:
Named Hortus Deliciarum (Latin for ‘Garden of Delights’), the new #GucciHighJewelry collection draws on the symbolic motifs that are dear to @alessandro_michele and Gucci, taken from the extensive and multifarious canon of House iconography. The saturated, hypnotic hues of a sky at sunset, the romanticism of a rose garden, and motifs from animal kingdom, evoking mythic bestiary and ancient fauna, are 
the ultimate source of inspiration for the new collection, including more than 130 pieces, mainly one of a kind.

node.title: The New Hortus Deliciarum High Jewelry Collection

node.text: The façade of the #GUCCIGAOK flagship store, designed by artist SeungMo Park @HANDLE, is inspired by an imaginary forest. The artist explores the interplay between light and shadow, and the application of wire netting layers results in a vivid symbolism, illustrating the boundaries between what is real and what is an illusion. Reflecting on the environmental issues of our time, the Park expresses the existence and non-existence of nature, his concerns of what can be lost, leaving only the illusion of what might be left. #AlessandroMichele

node.title: Artist SeungMo Park on creating the #GUCCIGAOK façade

Directed by artist, photographer and director #HarmonyKorine with creative direction by 
@alessandro_michele and art direction by #ChristopherSimmonds.

node.text:
Debuting in a special film co-directed by award-winning photographer and director @floriasigismondi and @alessandro_michele, Aria. A singular voice, taking its turn in the spotlight; in the Italian language, ‘air’. In his notes on the collection, the Creative Director calls it “a deep and ecstatic diving in everything we yearningly miss today… a jubilee of breath.” 
In the year of Gucci’s centenary, Alessandro Michele opens the locks of history, only to find a deeply personal vision of the mythology that surrounds the brand. Standing sentinel is the Savoy Club—a tribute to @thesavoylondon hotel where founder Guccio Gucci worked as a liftboy in his youth. Once inside, Aria’s “hacking lab made of incursions and metamorphoses”—from Alessandro Michele’s notes on the show—is unveiled, featuring elements from House heritage and designs from @demnagvasalia, Creative Director of @balenciaga, ultimately expressions of reverence and homage.
#GucciAria #AlessandroMichele 
Music:
The soundtrack, by Alessandro Michele and mixed by Lawrence Rothman, comprises a selection of songs featuring the word Gucci, speaking to the staying power of the Maison and how profusely it contributed to the vocabulary of pop culture.
Lil Pump ‘Gucci Gang’
(B. Murray/G. Garcia/G. G. Nealy)
Rick Ross feat. Future ‘Green Gucci Suit’
(R. Ross/A. Stewart/N. Wilburn/D. Hayes)
Bhad Bhabie ‘Gucci Flip Flops (feat. Lil Yachty)’
(M. McCollum/L. Jae/I. Whitlow/J. Muhammad/L. Porter/D. McCorkell/D. Bregoli/S. Gloade/J. Lowe)
Mier ‘Gucci On My Bag’
Die Antwoord, Dita Von Teese ‘Gucci Coochie’
(A. Du Toit/W. Jones/J. Nobrega/L. Muggard/Dita Von Teese)
Vitalic, feat. David Shaw and The Beat ‘Waiting For The Stars’
(P. Arbez/D. Shaw/J. Garraud)
The production of this video followed Health and Safety guidelines and Covid-related laws and regulations.
Bureau Veritas Italia monitored the set in which animals were present and verify that no animals were harmed.

node.text: The new #GucciEyewear campaign for Fall Winter 2021 features #NiNi @captainmiao sporting the new frames of the season. The inspiration for these glasses spans different eras, blending retro allure and contemporary sophistication in perfect harmony. Directed by Luo Yang @luoyangggg , creative direction by @alessandro_michele and art direction by #ChristopherSimmonds. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele

node.accessibility_caption: A shot of a model standing and leaning one hand on black office shelves with office equipment and multiple grey files on them, against the backdrop of a lake and green leafy trees, styled with short blonde hair in a side parting and wearing an ivory wool sweater with red and blue animal intarsia, and beige pants, carrying a beige and ebony GG canvas messenger bag with brown leather trim and brown leather buckle straps on the flap across-body.

node.text: Wool knitwear adorned with playful motifs alongside retro-inspired GG monogram accessories from the #GucciTowardsAutumn selection appear in images created with @condenast. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele

node.accessibility_caption: A shot of a model standing and leaning one hand on black office shelves with office equipment and multiple grey files on them, against the backdrop of a lake and green leafy trees, styled with short blonde hair in a side parting and wearing an ivory wool sweater with red and blue animal intarsia, and beige pants, carrying a beige and ebony GG canvas messenger bag with brown leather trim and brown leather buckle straps on the flap across-body.

A shot of two models lying with an open retro laptop between them in a brown wood rowing boat floating on a lake full of algae, (left to right) one holding a black retro cell phone to their ear, styled with long brown hair and bangs and wearing metal-rimmed sunglasses with brown lenses, a light blue wool sweater with flower intarsia, puff sleeves and ribbed trims, beige check pants, beige socks and black leather loafers with gold-toned Horsebit and chunky lug sole; the other styled with short blonde hair in a side parting and wearing a blue and ivory stripe knit scarf, an olive green jacket with Interlocking G patch and zip fastening, blue jeans and black leather lace-up boots with Interlocking G jacquard stripe and chunky lug sole.

A shot of two models smiling and looking at each other with office shelves and files in the background and a black desk with office equipment on it in the foreground, against the backdrop of green leafy trees, (left to right) one standing behind the desk, styled with long brown hair and bangs, wearing a blue knit cardigan with ivory and red trims, patch pockets and button fastening, and carrying a beige GG Canvas mini messenger bag with brown leather labels and brown leather trim on one shoulder; the other sitting on the desk, styled with braided natural hair and wearing an off-white dress with point collar and button front, and a long dark blue cashmere cardigan with gold-toned buttons, with a brown leather Gucci Diana bag with bamboo handles, decorative neon handle shapers, and gold-toned Double G hardware standing next to them.

node.text: Layering elements in the perfect look for a return to the office, wherever that may be. Discover more through link in bio. #GucciDiana #AlessandroMichele

node.accessibility_caption: A side-on shot of a model sitting in a grassy field with trees and a lake in the background, holding a white mug in one hand and an open retro laptop in the other, head turned towards the camera, styled with short wavy brown hair and wearing a blue argyle knit wool sweater with red GG embroidery inside white diamonds to resemble playing cards and red ribbed trims, and a black GG embossed leather backpack with front flap pocket and zip closure.

node.text: A series of images created in collaboration with @condenast showcases the #GucciTowardsAutumn selection that brings together warm knits, coats and GG accessories for a playful take on remote working. Discover more via link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele

node.accessibility_caption: A side-on shot of a model sitting in a grassy field with trees and a lake in the background, holding a white mug in one hand and an open retro laptop in the other, head turned towards the camera, styled with short wavy brown hair and wearing a blue argyle knit wool sweater with red GG embroidery inside white diamonds to resemble playing cards and red ribbed trims, and a black GG embossed leather backpack with front flap pocket and zip closure.

A shot of two models standing in front of an office chair and desk with a keyboard and CRT computer monitor on it, in a grassy field blooming with white flowers with trees in the background, (left to right) one styled with short natural hair and wearing a single breasted blue and white tartan wool coat with GG canvas lining, point collar and button fastening, light blue checked shirt, cropped blue jeans, beige socks, and brown leather loafers, carrying a grey and black GG canvas tote bag with leather handles and straps; the other styled with short wavy brown hair and wearing a double-breasted brown and beige herringbone wool goat with Gucci Eschatology label, peak lapel and front flap patch pockets, a light blue shirt, and wide-leg blue jeans.

A shot of two models on grass in front of a lake with trees in the background, in the setting of an outdoor office with a brown wood desk, CRT computer monitor with a plant in a green vase on it, and a red coat stand, (left to right) one sitting on the desk, styled with long brown hair and bangs, wearing oversize metal-rimmed glasses, an off-white dress with gold-toned chain with Interlocking G at the pockets, point collar, button front and short sleeves, sheer black tights and black leather knee-high riding boots; the other standing in front of the desk, styled with long black hair and bangs, wearing a red silk shirt with pussy bow collar and puff sleeves, a brown pleated midi skirt with side slit and leather and gold-toned chain belt with Double G, and burgundy leather and beige GG canvas knee-high riding boots with Gucci buckle detail.

node.text: Created in partnership with @condenast, a new set of images inspired by work set-ups in unexpected locations showcases the #GucciTowardsAutumn selection, imagined for the cooler season. Discover more via link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele

node.accessibility_caption: A close-up foot shot of a model lying on a brown wood rowing boat next to a brown wood desk with a white retro computer and red retro landline phone on it, with a body of water in the background, wearing blue denim jeans, beige socks and white leather Gucci Tennis 1977 sneakers with green and red Web stripe on the side, green grosgrain trim, Gucci Tennis 1977 label and GG motif on the rubber sole.

node.text: Inspired by new ways of working, a portfolio of images created with @condenast presents #GucciTowardsAutumn, a lineup of ready-to-wear pieces and accessories imagined for the cooler season. Discover more via link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele #GucciTennis1977

node.accessibility_caption: A close-up foot shot of a model lying on a brown wood rowing boat next to a brown wood desk with a white retro computer and red retro landline phone on it, with a body of water in the background, wearing blue denim jeans, beige socks and white leather Gucci Tennis 1977 sneakers with green and red Web stripe on the side, green grosgrain trim, Gucci Tennis 1977 label and GG motif on the rubber sole.

A shot of two models in a grassy field blooming with white flowers, with trees and a lake in the background, (left to right) one standing next to a retro-style desk with a computer, lamp and office equipment on it, leaning their arm on top of the CRT computer monitor with their head turned to look at the other model, styled with short natural hair, wearing a light brown jacket with leather Gucci vintage logo patch on the chest, point collar, button flap pockets, gathered hem and cuffs and zipper closure, an ivory wool sweater with red and blue animal intarsia, and ivory pants; the other sitting at the desk typing on the keyboard, styled with short blond hair in a side parting, wearing a blue wool sweater with red and yellow animal intarsia and blue pants.

A shot of two models standing next to each other and smiling in the sunshine, in front of a retro-style office cubicle with a desk and filing cabinet, with green leafy trees in the background, (left to right) one styled with long auburn hair and wearing a black and ivory poppy-print dress with point collar and button front, carrying a brick and sand coloured leather Gucci Horsebit 1955 shoulder bag with blue leather trim and gold-toned Horsebit at the front on one shoulder; the other styled with long black hair and bangs, holding flashcards in their hands, wearing oversize metal-rimmed glasses, a beige silk shirt with point collar and ivory and black check tweed pants, carrying a burgundy leather Jackie 1961 shoulder bag with blue leather trim and gold-toned hardware on one shoulder.

node.text: Appearing in a playful series of images created in collaboration with @condenast is #GucciTowardsAutumn, a new selection of ready-to-wear pieces and accessories to layer elements for the perfect look for a return to the office, wherever that may be. The lineup brings together warm knitwear and a fall color palette. Photography by @marknmarkn and styling by @olaoluebiti. Discover more via link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele #GucciBeloved #GucciJackie1961 #GucciHorsebit1955

node.text: Said to be used in elixirs and magical potions, White Gardenia is a silky floral scent blended with Jasmine Grandiflorum Absolute, a delicate flower with an exquisite ethereal bouquet, in Gucci Flora Gorgeous Gardenia. The joyful @guccibeauty signature also features a cheerful Pear Blossom accord and a touch of Brown Sugar to add sweetness to its sillage. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele #GucciBeauty #FloraFantasy
